He is going to come sliding down again.

12:32.291 --> 12:34.017
Shiva!

12:34.014 --> 12:36.581
Your mother is up to something there!

12:37.496 --> 12:44.388
'Shiva, Shiva, Shiva, Shiva,
Shiva, Shiva, Shiva, Shiva!'

12:45.305 --> 12:46.594
