through ten banyan trees.

32:34.172 --> 32:35.941
I call this the Sikander.

32:37.455 --> 32:38.657
The Pride of Swords.

32:45.384 --> 32:46.913
A wonderful sword.

32:47.186 --> 32:50.911
But forgive me, Aslam,
this cannot match our speed.

32:52.711 --> 32:53.879
How insulting!

32:57.395 --> 33:02.081
Spoken words and spilled blood
can never be taken back.

33:02.961 --> 33:07.450
Duel with my sword and
prove the worth of your words.

33:35.273 --> 33:37.195
Does that prove
my point, Kattappa?

33:59.817 --> 34:01.467
I have traveled
across the world

34:01.460 --> 34:03.229
China, Persia, Mongolia, Greece.

34:03.782 --> 34:05.792
