will stay tied to this land.

35:12.130 --> 35:17.297
If loyalty has a face,
it is you, Kattappa.

35:18.776 --> 35:20.426
If you ever need anything...

35:20.698 --> 35:23.309
please don't ever forget that
you have a life-long friend.

35:47.445 --> 35:48.613
Vaishali.

35:50.689 --> 35:52.295
Where are you going?
- I will be right back.

37:35.433 --> 37:36.755
We have a golden opportunity

37:36.915 --> 37:38.564
to fulfill the oath
we have taken.

37:38.837 --> 37:41.884
They are celebrating
Bhallaladeva's birthday

37:41.880 --> 37:43.769
on the next new moon.

37:44.242 --> 37:46.689
The entire kingdom will be busy
with the celebrations.

37:49.007 --> 37:51.050
The opportunity to
free Queen Devasena...

37:51.049 --> 37:54.774
