to my boiling blood.

38:58.716 --> 39:01.688
If you can feel their intensity

39:03.802 --> 39:05.243
then let me go.

39:14.051 --> 39:16.542
You have to leave in two days.
So get ready.

39:16.975 --> 39:19.225
