01:54:35.089 --> 01:54:37.175
the Kalakeyas wouldn't
expect it either.

01:54:37.331 --> 01:54:39.460
That is why
we should implement it.

01:54:39.613 --> 01:54:42.737
I second the plan.
- I approve it.

01:54:43.817 --> 01:54:47.422
It is the only way
into our kingdom.

01:54:47.581 --> 01:54:52.715
