the perfect solution. - Yes.

01:56:15.029 --> 01:56:18.437
Divide the rest of the army
equally between the Princes!

01:56:20.434 --> 01:56:22.203
Bhalla, Baahu.

01:56:22.756 --> 01:56:25.683
